name: Latte
description: This is Latte! He is an elderly Great Dane! He came in with two siblings, the Chihuahuas, Mocha and Coco. He is so sweet and follow you wherever you go. Latte is well trained, and house broken. He is just looking for his forever home to rest in. He also has cancer on his leg.
'This is Tip-Toe! She is a husky! She is very well behaved and is house-broken. I am quiet and well-behaved.'

name: 'Georgie'
description: This is Georgie! She is a 1 year old Coon Hound! She is incredibly playful and vocal! She wants a person to play in the yard with! She is very loyal and smart!

name: 'Gidget'
description: This is Gidget! She is a Belgian Malinois/Pitbull mix! She is very sweet and loving! She is a little nervous of new people, but she warms up fast and loves love! She needs someone that she can trust for the rest of her life! She needs a life long pal and a forever best friend!

name: Polly
description: This is Polly! She is a 4 year old Staffie mix! She is full of fun and loves to play! She does really well with kids and has the prettiest face! We like to call her our “Pot-belly pig”!

name: Bandit
description: This is Bandit! She is a 2 year old Husky. She is very vocal and walks great on a leash. She likes to be around people and she is good with some dogs, and not with others. She is a big goofball!

name: 'Spice'
description: This is Spice! He is a 5 month old domestic short hair tabby. He is a feral kitty that we are working on to build his trust. He occasionally gives us the scared airplane ears, but he is learning to be picked up and loved. He needs someone to spend more time with him, showing him how nice humans can be. He DOES NOT like to be handled.
